track_notes: Cars are parked frequently around the Haggenegg col. Full trail around Haggenegg via Bannegg. The Hochstuckli summit can be seen and accessed much earlier from the east, but this is widely private property and discouraged by signs. The property can be bypassed more to the north indeed, see Swisstopo map.
Winter hike. Snowshoes were not needed, because solid tracks have been made by backcountry skiers and snowshoe hikers. Five days since last snowfall.
I accidentally left the trail due to snow in the section between Mostelberg and Jansern.
